  "content": "<p data-pid=\"dqhcPu8z\">西安中学在装修的同时，收费，提早开学，校园内粉尘极大的情况下，还检测出甲醛超标，B 站搜索西安中学有相关视频，以下是听说：</p><p data-pid=\"u-R9Yoir\">学生尝试过罢课等行为，但是没有效果，学校报警后有学生被拘留，原因是造谣，市环保局和市委的人也去过但是没有任何效果，目前正在尝试通过组织更大范围的罢课等行为扩大影响，已有多名学生进医院，多名学生确诊白血病。</p><p data-pid=\"I3mtLpa4\">从头到尾没停过课，但是可以请假，年级主任辞职。我在西安中学的朋友上周在医院，可能还有他不知道的消息，这周开始家长也要求他去上学了。</p><p data-pid=\"UQRNt3-y\">他说估计没机会了，就这样了。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-22edb3f3f291b89cc8c4578afb1e5fb3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"574\" data-rawheight=\"1200\" data-original-token=\"v2-22edb3f3f291b89cc8c4578afb1e5fb3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-0f98186613f0b645162b300a8c5ad261_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"574\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-22edb3f3f291b89cc8c4578afb1e5fb3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;574&#39; height=&#39;1200&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"574\" data-rawheight=\"1200\" data-original-token=\"v2-22edb3f3f291b89cc8c4578afb1e5fb3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-0f98186613f0b645162b300a8c5ad261_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"574\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-22edb3f3f291b89cc8c4578afb1e5fb3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-22edb3f3f291b89cc8c4578afb1e5fb3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-65a9119260ca87a5653ee143c17b50da_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"843\" data-rawheight=\"1200\" data-original-token=\"v2-65a9119260ca87a5653ee143c17b50da\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bc114d5d98be2249a8b4b2b8512906f8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"843\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-65a9119260ca87a5653ee143c17b50da_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;843&#39; height=&#39;1200&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"843\" data-rawheight=\"1200\" data-original-token=\"v2-65a9119260ca87a5653ee143c17b50da\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bc114d5d98be2249a8b4b2b8512906f8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"843\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-65a9119260ca87a5653ee143c17b50da_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-65a9119260ca87a5653ee143c17b50da_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-8298795cdba93a83be866523fd37f6ab_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1587\" data-rawheight=\"1002\" data-original-token=\"v2-8298795cdba93a83be866523fd37f6ab\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-41b11225788d1e37e0f49b59cd0e4eab_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1587\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8298795cdba93a83be866523fd37f6ab_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1587&#39; height=&#39;1002&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1587\" data-rawheight=\"1002\" data-original-token=\"v2-8298795cdba93a83be866523fd37f6ab\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-41b11225788d1e37e0f49b59cd0e4eab_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1587\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8298795cdba93a83be866523fd37f6ab_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-8298795cdba93a83be866523fd37f6ab_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f8e26b1b78f3921b51a9935876e32acf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1062\" data-rawheight=\"1294\" data-original-token=\"v2-f8e26b1b78f3921b51a9935876e32acf\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f01409f5b39a827922383df374c671a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1062\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f8e26b1b78f3921b51a9935876e32acf_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1062&#39; height=&#39;1294&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1062\" data-rawheight=\"1294\" data-original-token=\"v2-f8e26b1b78f3921b51a9935876e32acf\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f01409f5b39a827922383df374c671a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1062\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f8e26b1b78f3921b51a9935876e32acf_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f8e26b1b78f3921b51a9935876e32acf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><hr/><p data-pid=\"OSBA6qAk\">我错了，我错的离谱，我大错特错。这哪里是监狱啊，这简直是奴隶制。</p><p data-pid=\"mRkeHSwK\">学生的力量还是太小了，但他们正在组织起来。南京的学子们失败了<sup data-text=\"如何看待南京高中生「反卷联盟」运动及其失败？\" data-url=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/664573731/answer/3597882375\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>，西安的学子们也可能要失败了。敌人们太强大了，他们还相互勾结。必须进一步改进斗争策略，才能在学校、政府和家长的围剿下找到一丝胜机。</p><p data-pid=\"HELtYLIG\">这个问题肯定又被压热度了，就如之前那个南京的问题已经荒原了一样。我这篇回答估计也活不了多久，但让更多人知道这件事，总是有帮助的。</p><p data-pid=\"iBApdyT-\">顺带@一下之前在南京的问题下回答的朋友： <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/1b0d7514aae68770940392df2fcf90e5\" data-hash=\"1b0d7514aae68770940392df2fcf90e5\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$1b0d7514aae68770940392df2fcf90e5\">@大白兔奶糖</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/25608bc03821ad469556f777de36da9b\" data-hash=\"25608bc03821ad469556f777de36da9b\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$25608bc03821ad469556f777de36da9b\">@一直住顶楼</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/551be2b846c215e2440bc271817a7726\" data-hash=\"551be2b846c215e2440bc271817a7726\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$551be2b846c215e2440bc271817a7726\">@大萌饼王毛文龙</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/985c449a94e4e68618047fd6b4d36e59\" data-hash=\"985c449a94e4e68618047fd6b4d36e59\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$985c449a94e4e68618047fd6b4d36e59\">@Wind 小号</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/792d2f3c81d3e328a22a2760ee5395e5\" data-hash=\"792d2f3c81d3e328a22a2760ee5395e5\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$792d2f3c81d3e328a22a2760ee5395e5\">@想上分的木乃伊</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/9949570ae885e446be08ac31659ddb16\" data-hash=\"9949570ae885e446be08ac31659ddb16\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$9949570ae885e446be08ac31659ddb16\">@skywalkerplayer</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/84dad7493185a9480473e511d2595800\" data-hash=\"84dad7493185a9480473e511d2595800\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$84dad7493185a9480473e511d2595800\">@王左政</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/307cb5c7d1b929256b83629ce2b6e98d\" data-hash=\"307cb5c7d1b929256b83629ce2b6e98d\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$307cb5c7d1b929256b83629ce2b6e98d\">@绮风</a> ，希望都可以来关注一下这件事情。</p>",
